e-search-game&quot;>;周一报道&lt;/a>;，消息人士称 OpenAI 已经.. .&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153767/sam-altman-openai-google-io-search-engine-launch&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153767/sam-altman-openai-google-io-search-engine-launch" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153767/sam-altman-openai-google-io-search-engine-launch</id><author><name>凯莉罗宾逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-10T14:13:53-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-10T14:13:53-04:00</updated><title>如何观看本周末可能出现的北极光</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;冰岛上空的北极光&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/H-V9vpPqw2BxnsZ2AwRiNGRAZ7c=/0x0:6000x4000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/73339699/2118359708.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;如果您有幸在本周末目睹极光，智能手机摄像头将提供比您自己的眼睛更好的视野。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Owen Humphreys/PA Images via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;eE4oBv&quot;>;本周末仰望天空的人可能会见证通常只有北极附近地区才有的宇宙视觉体验圆圈。全球多个气象机构报告称，由于异常强烈的太阳耀斑，未来几天南至阿拉巴马州和北加利福尼亚州都可以看到北极光。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;MXz5GE&quot;>;周四，国家海洋局和大气管理局 (NOAA) 发布了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.swpc.noaa.gov/news/swpc-issues-its-first-g4-watch-2005&quot;>;G4 地磁风暴监视&lt;/a>; ——近 20 年来首次宣布。 G4 地磁风暴（第二强，被认为“严重”）可能会干扰电力基础设施和导航系统，但它们也可能引发北极光。这意味着世界部分地区可以...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153694/how-to-watch-aurora-borealis- g4-地磁风暴-noaa&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153694/how-to-watch-aurora-borealis-g4-geomagnetic-storm-noaa" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153694/how-to-watch-aurora-borealis-g4-geotropic-storm-noaa</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry></feed>